<H2><font color=purple><i>Papers</i></font></H2> <p> High-quality research
papers, describing original ideas on the fundamental aspects of all forms of
database systems and technology, are solicited.  Accepted papers will be
presented as a talk at the conference.  <font color=red>Submissions should be
at most twelve pages long, using reasonable font size and page layout.</font>


