<H2><font color=purple><i>Submission Instructions</i></font></H2>

The submission procedure is electronic, and is a two-step process. First, the
authors will register their paper at the submission server. Second, after
registration the authors will get an automatic reply containing a URL where
they can upload their PostScript or PDF file.  <font color=red>Registration
will be open on June 7, 2002</font>. Paper submission will be open on June
7. Please, visit the ICDT 2003 home page at http://www.dis.uniroma1.it/icdt03
to submit papers.

